TdhZones - local version

On an Android device:

Uninstall any previous version of TdhZones.

Using a browser on your mobile device, navigate to the TdhZones website.

Click on the Software Packages link and download TdhZones.apk. Exit the browser. 

Go to Settings | Apps | Downloaded. Select and install TdhZones.



TdhZonesC - client version

On an Android device:

Uninstall any previous version of TdhZonesC.

Using a browser on your mobile device, navigate to the TdhZones website.

Click on the Software Packages link and download TdhZonesC.apk. Exit the browser. 

Go to Settings | Apps | Downloaded. Select and install TdhZonesC.



TdhZones - server program

From a pc running MS Windows or Linux:

Navigate to the TdhZones website. click on the Software Packages link.

Download and open either the TdhZones_win or TdhZones_linux64 file.

For the TdhZones_win file.  execute the install program and follow the installation procedure.

For the TdhZones_linux64 file: extract the files to a directory of your choosing.   

